</div></div></div></div><div id="articleSlideshow" class="article-slideshow carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="false"><div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox"><div class="article-slide carousel-item active"><img width="476" height="720" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20476%20720'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-1080x720 size-1080x720" alt data-lazy-srcset="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-Baume.jpg 723w, https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-Baume-508x768.jpg 508w, https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-Baume-200x302.jpg 200w, https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-Baume-397x600.jpg 397w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 476px) 100vw, 476px" data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-Baume.jpg" /><noscript><img width="476" height="720" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-Baume.jpg" class="attachment-1080x720 size-1080x720" alt="" srcset="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-Baume.jpg 723w, https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-Baume-508x768.jpg 508w, https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-Baume-200x302.jpg 200w, https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-Baume-397x600.jpg 397w" sizes="(max-width: 476px) 100vw, 476px" /></noscript><div class=" carousel-caption --width  d-block">
<h5>Image 1 of 28</h5>
