<div class="article-contributor-photo-section background-grey background-box-shadow --bottom">
<div class="container">
<div class="row article-contributor-photo-reverse">
<div class="col-12 col-md-8 flex --direction-col --justify-content-center article-contributor-main">
<div class="article-contributor__meta-container">
<h1 class="article-contributor-section_title">Sara Baume</h1>
<p class="article-contributor-section_content">Sara Baume is the author of three novels, <i>Spill Simmer Falter Wither</i>, <em>A Line Made by Walking</em> and <em>Seven Steeples</em>, and one book of non-fiction, <em>Handiwork</em>. She lives and works on the south coast Ireland.<br><br><em>Photograph  Keith OHalloran</em></p>
<a class="article-contributor-section_link" href="https://granta.com/sara-baume">More about the author </a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-12 col-md-4  article-contributor-image ">
<div class="article-contributor__img-container">
<div data-bg="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Sara-Baume-_c_Keith-OHalloran.croppedjpg.jpg" class="article-contributor-photo-section-photo rocket-lazyload" data-background="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Sara-Baume-_c_Keith-OHalloran.croppedjpg.jpg" style></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
