<div class="dnd_post-card__lower-section">
<h2 class="dnd_post-card_title">
<a href="https://granta.com/the-hair-baby/">
The Hair Baby
</a>
</h2>
<h4 class="dnd_post-card_author">
<a class="contributor-link" href="https://granta.com/contributor/sara-baume/">Sara Baume</a>
</h4>
<p class="dnd_post-card_text">
She has been ten for a month and she does not like it. She carries the weight of her extra digit like a chain-mail vest.<br/><br/>Fiction by Sara Baume.
</p>
</div>
